      <h3>Basic Sales Commission</h3>
      
      <p>Your commission depends on how many units are sold and installed in the same month:</p>
      
      <ul>
      <li><strong>1–4 units:</strong> RM300/unit</li>
      
      <li><strong>5–9 units:</strong> RM350/unit</li>
      
      <li><strong>10–14 units:</strong>&nbsp;RM450/unit</li>
      
      <li><strong>15+ units:</strong>&nbsp;RM500/unit</li>
      </ul>
      
      <p><strong>Example:</strong> Sell 5 units → 5 x RM350 = RM1,750 commission.</p>
      
      <h3>Cuckoo Morning Meeting (CMM) Incentive (Not Compulsary)</h3>
      
      <p>Attend CMM every Tuesday &amp; Friday at your nearest Training Hub and earn extra incentives:</p>
      
      <ul>
      <li>3 units → +RM200</li>
      
      <li>6 units → +RM400</li>
      
      <li>10 units → +RM700</li>
      
      <li>15 units → +RM1,000</li>
      </ul>
      
      <p>❗ Please take note that if you sell Cuckoo products but don’t attend CMM, you only get the sales commission withot the CMM incentive. </p>
      
